.DT
set_default_language
Disk World creator help
set_default_language

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_default_language -  This method sets the default language to use for the person.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_default_language(string def)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^def%^RESET%^ - the default language

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/communicate.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the default language to use for the person.  The default
language is their native tongue, so things in this language show as
not being a special language.
.EP

